review_blob:
This was one of my first favorites.  Spend several afternoons drinking from a six of this.  I have contacted BM asking them to start brewing this again.

It was good.

O.K. this id the most hops for the price.  A very goof PA.  Almost an IPA.

If you havent tried this.  I think you ought to.  Especially, if you dont live in a beer-rich area.
